"You're still thinking like a maximal, you've already said that 
that's not what we are." he looked at her new form," We've become 
some type of mutant, We can barely consider ourselves as translife 
forms any more." His thinking was beginning to match Veratis' they no 
longer fit in with normal transformer society. 

Veratis came over the comm, "Play Times over, Lunarpine, Razor Claw, 
and Ice report to the briefing room for class.

(I'll send the class then I got to go. try not to have to much fun 
without me)
